OL,3,C'Gething deserved better': Drakeford
OL,4,Con successor's time as First Minister
OL,6,FHe said: "I thought Vaughan deserved
OL,7,Fmuch better.
OL,9,F"I think he was well prepared to be a
OL,10,FFirst Minister. I think that he would
OL,11,Fhave been a very good First Minister,
OL,12,Fand it is that hubristic sense you
OL,13,Fget, isn't it, is that somehow the
OL,14,Fthing that in the end made it all
OL,15,Funwind was a decision he himself made
OL,16,Fthat was the wrong decision, but he
OL,17,Fdefinitely deserved better."
