OL,3,C'Gething deserved better': Drakeford
OL,4,Con successor's time as First Minister
OL,6,FMr Gething received #200,000 in a
OL,7,Fcampaign donation by the director of
OL,8,FDauson Environmental Group Ltd, David
OL,9,FNeal, who was convicted twice for
OL,10,Fenvironmental offences.
OL,12,FNeal was given a suspended prison
OL,13,Fsentence in 2013 for illegally dumping
OL,14,Fwaste on a conservation site on the
OL,15,FGwent Levels. His companies Atlantic
OL,16,FRecycling and Neal Soil Suppliers were
OL,17,Falso prosecuted and ordered to pay
OL,18,Ffines and costs of #202,000.
