OL,3,C'Gething deserved better': Drakeford
OL,4,Con successor's time as First Minister
OL,6,FThere have also been concerns about a
OL,7,Fpossible conflict of interest in the
OL,8,Fmoney coming from a company which was
OL,9,Floaned #400,000 by the Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment-owned Development Bank of
OL,11,FWales (DBW).
OL,13,FThe loan from the DBW was given to
OL,14,FNeal Soil Suppliers ` a subsidiary of
OL,15,FDauson ` in 2023 to help purchase a
OL,16,Fsolar farm, at a time when Mr Gething
OL,17,Fwas Economy Minister.
