OL,3,C'Gething deserved better': Drakeford
OL,4,Con successor's time as First Minister
OL,6,FMr Gething has always insisted that he
OL,7,Fcannot take any decision relating to
OL,8,FDauson ` which is based in his
OL,9,Fconstituency ` and the DBW is entirely
OL,10,Findependent of ministers.
OL,12,FHis four months in the top job also
OL,13,Fsaw a row over a leaked phone message,
OL,14,Fwhich led to him sacking one of his
OL,15,Fministers and Plaid Cymru's withdrawal
OL,16,Fof support for his Government.
OL,18,FAlthough still a Member of the Senedd,
OL,19,Fhe has since kept a low profile,
OL,20,Fopting not to take a position in the
OL,21,Fcabinet.
