OL,3,C'Gething deserved better': Drakeford
OL,4,Con successor's time as First Minister
OL,6,FSharp End's Rob Osborne asked fellow
OL,7,Fformer First Minister Mark Drakeford:
OL,8,F"There is life after being First
OL,9,FMinister - should he get back out
OL,10,Fthere and do something now?"
OL,12,F"I hope he will," Drakeford said.
OL,14,F"I hope he'll find something that he
OL,15,Fwants to do and enjoys doing.
OL,17,F"I don't think if what had happened to
OL,18,Fhim had happened to me, I don't think
OL,19,FI'd ever want to set foot in here (The
OL,20,FSenedd) again. But he comes very
OL,21,Fregularly. He speaks in debates.
