OL,3,C'Gething deserved better': Drakeford
OL,4,Con successor's time as First Minister
OL,6,F"He's very good at all of that. And he
OL,7,Fmust be, you know, a lot of it must be
OL,8,Flooking ahead, must it? And hoping to
OL,9,Ffind something worthwhile that will
OL,10,Fuse his very real talent."
OL,12,FIn September last year, Mr Gething
OL,13,Fannounced he would be stepping down at
OL,14,Fthe next Senedd election. The former
OL,15,Flawyer has represented Cardiff South
OL,16,Fand Penarth in the Senedd since 2011
OL,17,Fand had served as Economy Minister and
OL,18,FHealth Minister in Mark Drakeford's
OL,19,FGovernment during the pandemic.
